Package nars.gui

Graphical user interface of the system

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    BagWindow<BagType extends Item>
    JWindow display the priority distribution of items within a given bag
    ConceptWindow
    JWindow displaying the content of a Concept, such as beliefs, goals, and questions
    InferenceRecorder
    Inference log, which record input/output of each inference step interface with 1 implementation: GUI ( batch not implemented )
    InferenceWindow
    JWindow displaying inference log
    InputWindow
    Input window, accepting user tasks
    MainWindow
    Main window of NARS GUI
    MessageDialog
    Pop-up message for the user to accept
    NarsFrame
    Specify shared properties of NARS windows
    ParameterWindow
    JWindow displaying a system parameter that can be adjusted in run time
    TermWindow
    JWindow accept a Term, then display the content of the corresponding Concept

Package nars.gui Description

Graphical user interface of the system

Package Specification

All windows extend NarsFrame, with MessageDialog as the only exception.
